{"tid":2075205,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【武漢肺炎】譚德塞：大流行影響將持續數十年　政治化、國家不團結加劇疫情","createTime":"2020-06-22T16:24:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T16:31:26.000Z","uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"853076d4ecc0cedc4423808937ffae8244f2b6d9","tid":2075205,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T16:24:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Layer201_rOdev_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FLayer201_rOdev_1200x0.png&h=9c374a3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情在世界各國持續，除拉丁美洲國家，如巴西的疫情繼續蔓延外，在亞洲，南韓亦承認出現第二波疫情。世界衞生組織總幹事譚德塞 (Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus) 在一個視像論壇上，表示全球大流行仍在加劇，又表示疫情的影響會持續數十年。<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞周一（22 日）在杜拜舉行的視像健康論壇上發表演說，指全球大流行仍在蔓延，而且其影響將會在未來數十年內持續，「全球大流行不止是健康危機，也是經濟和社會危機，在許多國家也是政治危機。」<br />\n<br />\n至今武漢肺炎已經在全球感染近 900 萬人，且造成接近 50 萬人死亡。譚德塞指，武肺肆虐是因為全球缺乏團結，「我們不能在分裂的世界中戰勝這種流行病。」他又認為，全球大流行出現「政治化」，而政治化亦加劇了大流行。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thestandnews.com/politics/武漢肺炎-譚德塞-大流行影響將持續數十年-政治化-國家不團結加劇疫情/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E8%AD%9A%E5%BE%B7%E5%A1%9E-%E5%A4%A7%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%8C%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E5%B0%87%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E6%95%B8%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%B4-%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%8C%96-%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E4%B8%8D%E5%9C%98%E7%B5%90%E5%8A%A0%E5%8A%87%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%2F&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7hVTfDkzAunSCULMKrq9Td0%3D&h=8eb53101\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E8%AD%9A%E5%BE%B7%E5%A1%9E-%E5%A4%A7%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%8C%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E5%B0%87%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E6%95%B8%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%B4-%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%8C%96-%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E4%B8%8D%E5%9C%98%E7%B5%90%E5%8A%A0%E5%8A%87%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%2F&h=f5078aa7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.thestandnews.com/politics/武漢肺炎-譚德塞-大流行影響將持續數十年-政治化-國家不團結加劇疫情/</a>"},{"pid":"b8b047ce4652ef01e72349879a2fda3efe7fbf2a","tid":2075205,"uid":28114,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T16:25:33.000Z","msg":"收爹啦力架<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/11/225834_813edb86f0695bd8e83e9745ee5ea21f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F11%2F225834_813edb86f0695bd8e83e9745ee5ea21f.png&h=019fd54b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb290758a0fb262e2d68e9b056e54eb881f8c9be","tid":2075205,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T16:27:18.000Z","msg":"最應該負責嘅出嚟鳩噏甩鍋"},{"pid":"479028aacb82fe91b7d30da208aa1f97c8d85fd2","tid":2075205,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T16:30:32.000Z","msg":"講到唔關自己事咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cb2da80f5d8395dd53d08f2fe11fda448a94e19","tid":2075205,"uid":119232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T16:31:26.000Z","msg":"邊個話冇大流行先"}]}